NG0569:1: dz+nyan badzra ma ha ba la ti /
NG0569:4: ma ha kro ti shwa ri dz+nya na d+ha ki ni prad nya da du badzra da ra /
NG0569:5: om ru lu ru lu hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:11: sarba ma ha badzra kro d+hi /
NG0569:12: ka ya badzra kri ta ya /
NG0569:16: na mahsarba ta tha ga te b+h+yo /
NG0569:17: bi sha mu khe b+h+yahsarba tha khang ud ga te /
NG0569:18: s+pha ra na i mam ga ga na kham swa ha /
NG0569:19: om shri badzra ra ga d+hu pe du /
NG0569:24: pu tsa me g+ha sa mu dra s+pha ra na sa ma ye swa ha /
NG0569:26: sarba ta tha ga ta ma ha pany+tsa a mri ta /
NG0569:27: rba na kha ram hri ka sa badzra si ti om /
NG0569:30: om na ma sarba ta tha ga ta /
NG0569:31: ma ha pu tsa me ka ya ra na /
NG0569:32: badzra swa b+ha wa ad ma ko\u0f85ham /
NG0569:41: ma ha me tha maha pan tsa a mri ta /
NG0569:42: kha hi kha hi kha hi /
NG0569:46: sa ma ya kha ha ho /
NG0569:47: i dam ma ha ba ling ta /
NG0569:52: sa ma ya hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:53: sha ra lam ga tsa me /
NG0569:54: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa mngon par rtogs pa'i rgyud las /
NG0569:55: 'phrin las rim pa'i le'u ste dgu brgya gnyis pa'o
NG0569:56: // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen pos rnal
NG0569:58: rang bzhin rnam dag chos nyid las //
NG0569:59: dpal chen khro rgyal he ru ka / ye shes lnga yi dbang bskur zhing *//
NG0569:60: sku gsung thugs su byin gyis brlabs //
NG0569:61: khro chung khrab chags bzhin du brtan nas //
NG0569:62: thugs khar 'khor lo rtsibs brgyad dang *//
NG0569:63: rdo rje rtse dgu kha gdengs dang *//
NG0569:65: pad+ma 'dab brgyad dbang gi cho ga / rdo rje rgya gram ljang khu gnas //
NG0569:66: ye shes sems dpa' rigs kyi mdog / zhal gcig phyag gnyis khro bo'i sku //
NG0569:67: mthu mar rang sngags 'phreng ba dang *//
NG0569:68: bsgom dbyangs yi ge 'bru brgyad gsal //
NG0569:69: ye shes lnga yi 'od zer gyis //
NG0569:70: chos kyi dbyings nyid rab 'byams su //
NG0569:71: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs la thim //
NG0569:72: mchod phul rgyud bskul dngos grub bsdus //
NG0569:73: byang chub sems dpa' 'gro don bskul //
NG0569:74: sems can sgo gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:76: lus ngag yid gsum sgrib pa sbyangs //
NG0569:77: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rdzogs //
NG0569:78: mgal me'i 'khor lo bzhin du bsgom //
NG0569:79: mchod dang bstod pa sum yar bya //
NG0569:80: tshogs kyi 'khor lo ci nus bskor //
NG0569:81: de ltar gsang sngags bzlas tshur ni //
NG0569:82: rang rang sngags dang bsgom dbyangs brgyad //
NG0569:83: tshom bu thig le stong brgya bcu //
NG0569:84: gtso 'khor dag kyang de bzhin no //
NG0569:85: dril ba'i snying po kun la bsdeb //
NG0569:86: 'di ltar ma yengs bsgom bzlas na //
NG0569:88: nas ring po mi thogs par //
NG0569:89: ngo mtshar drod rtags nges par 'byung *//
NG0569:90: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub blang *//
NG0569:93: om d+harma ka ya shu dz+nya ta dz+nya /
NG0569:95: bud d+ha ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha kro d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:96: om badzra ka ya a ta ri sha dz+nya na mo ta /
NG0569:97: badzra ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha tsan d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:98: om sam bo ka ya sa man ta dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:99: rat+ta ma ha shri he ru ka ma ha u kra ya hu~m phat /
NG0569:100: om bo d+hi ka ya pra ta ba sha dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:101: pad+ma ma ha shri he ru ka maha kri ta hu~m phat /
NG0569:102: om nir ma ka ya krin da dz+nya na mo ta na /
NG0569:103: karma maha shri he ru ka ma ha rak+sha hu~m phat /
NG0569:104: om bud d+ha thad ra pradz+nya da du ma ha kro d+hi shwa ri ni hu~m phat /
NG0569:105: badzra rat+na pad+ma karma da ra pradz+nya da du ma ha kro d+ha shwa ri hu~m phat /
NG0569:106: hu~m ya man ta krid pa tsa pa tsa phat /
NG0569:107: hu~m pad mam ta kr-id hu lu hu lu phat /
NG0569:108: hu~m bi g+h+nan ta krid tshin d+ha tshin d+ha hu~m phat /
NG0569:109: om d+harma d+ha du dz+nyi na ka ya ma ha
NG0569:110: bi ra shri he ru ka badzra ma ha kro
NG0569:112: prad dz+nya ma ha kro d+hi sho ri /
NG0569:113: badzra kro d+ha ma ha pa la ti /
NG0569:117: om ru lu ru lu hu~m b+h+yo hu~m /
NG0569:118: khro rgyal yab yum la sogs te /
NG0569:119: thams cad 'dus pa'i snying po sngags /
NG0569:121: byin brlabs dpag med sangs rgyas sa /
NG0569:123: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa don gyi snying po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:124: bsam gtan gsang sngags kyi le'u ste dgu brgya gsum
NG0569:125: pa'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen gyis
NG0569:126: / mthar thug de kho na nyid bshad /
NG0569:127: om ye shes lhun grub nyid /
NG0569:128: a zhes chos dbyings ye shes te //
NG0569:129: rnam par snang mdzad de ni rigs //
NG0569:130: khro rgyal bud d+ha he ru ka zla tshes mnyam nyid ye shes te //
NG0569:131: rnam par snang mdzad de bzhin rigs //
NG0569:132: khro rgyal rat+na he ru ka rna ru kunartog ye shes te //
NG0569:133: snang ba mtha' yas pad+ma'i rigs //
NG0569:134: khro rgyal pad+ma he ru ka / thig le me long ye shes te //
NG0569:135: rdo rje sems dpa' rdo rje'i rigs //
NG0569:136: khro rgyal badzra he ru ka bya ba grub pa'i ye shes te //
NG0569:137: don yod grub pa las kyi rigs //
NG0569:138: khro rgyal karma he ru ka / rang 'byung ye shes rang shar ba'o //
NG0569:139: sa rus sangs rgyas spyan nyid de //
NG0569:140: bud d+ha kro d+hi shwa ri'o //
NG0569:141: khrag chu ma ma ki nyid ni //
NG0569:143: me dang drod ni gos dkar mo //
NG0569:144: pad ma kro d+hi shwa ri'o //
NG0569:145: rlung 'byung dam tshig sgrol ma ste //
NG0569:147: rnam rig nam mkha'i dbyings phyug ma /
NG0569:149: 'byung ba chen po ye sangs rgyas //
NG0569:150: de ni phung po skye mched khams //
NG0569:151: gdod nas sangs rgyas ye shes lha //
NG0569:152: rang gnas dkyil 'khor rtogs par bya //
NG0569:153: rtogs mchog ma spangs gnas su dag / sangs rgyas thams cad 'dus pa yis //
NG0569:154: snying po'i thig le gsang sngags kyis //
NG0569:155: sangs rgyas dkyil 'khor ma lus pa //
NG0569:158: chen khro rgyal dpal chen he ru ka / mtshan don lhun grub chos rnams rdzogs //
NG0569:159: he zhes dngos med byang chub sems //
NG0569:160: chos nyid ma bcos rnam dag dbyings //
NG0569:161: sgrib med ye shes rab gsal bas //
NG0569:162: thams cad der rdzogs dgyes pa che //
NG0569:163: ru zhes thugs rje kun la khyab //
NG0569:164: rang bzhin thugs kyi mnyam nyid las //
NG0569:165: dmigs pa med cing phyogs rigs bral //
NG0569:166: chags med chags mchog rgyal po'o //
NG0569:167: ka zhes rol pa cir yang snang *//
NG0569:168: sna tshogs rang snang ngos bzung med //
NG0569:169: thabs mkhas 'phrin las rnam mang bas //
NG0569:170: 'gro don sna tshogs so sor mdzad //
NG0569:171: de bzhin gshegs pa kun gyi thugs //
NG0569:172: dngos po rnam dag ma bcos pa //
NG0569:173: dngos med mu mtha' med pa nyid //
NG0569:174: rang bzhin stong chen mtha' yas 'das //
NG0569:175: 'dus ma byas pa'i chos dbyings de //
NG0569:176: chos dbyings kro d+hi shwa ri ste //
NG0569:177: gnyis med bde chen byang chub sems //
NG0569:178: dbyings nyid ye shes dbyer med pas //
NG0569:179: dpal chen ye shes mtshan rdzogs pa'o //
NG0569:181: gnyis med byang chub sems su gsal //
NG0569:182: snying po byang chub sems nyid de //
NG0569:183: rgya ma chad cing phyogs ma lhung *//
NG0569:184: rang byung ye shes rang gsal bas //
NG0569:185: skye med 'gag med thog mtha' med //
NG0569:186: rang byung kun khyab 'dus ma byas //
NG0569:188: de nyid dpal chen he ru ka / lhun grub rang rig ye shes gnyis //
NG0569:189: ma 'gags rang snang gnyis med pa'o //
NG0569:191: rig pa brdal khyab ma bcos pa //
NG0569:192: phyogs med rang snang snying po ste //
NG0569:194: ru lu 'khor ba'i rnam shes brgyad //
NG0569:195: / gnas kyi ma mo ki ri brgyad //
NG0569:196: ma spangs gnas dag rang bzhin te //
NG0569:197: chos nyid byang chub sems nyid gsal //
NG0569:198: ru lu yul brgyad snang srid chos //
NG0569:199: ye nas gnas dag 'phra men brgyad //
NG0569:200: skye med rnam dag chos nyid de //
NG0569:201: mtha' la 'das pa'i chos nyid do //
NG0569:202: hu~m ni yul sems rang snang kun //
NG0569:203: byang chub sems nyid rang snang bas //
NG0569:204: he ru ka dpal ngo bo nyid //
NG0569:205: gnyis med byang chub sems su gcig / b+h+yo /
NG0569:206: sna tshogs rig pa'i rang bzhin te //
NG0569:207: rig pa stong gsal ma 'gags shar //
NG0569:208: de nyid dbang phyug nyi shu brgyad //
NG0569:211: sna tshogs cir snang de bzhin nyid //
NG0569:212: ma bcos rang snang ji bzhin nyid //
NG0569:213: phyag rgya bzhi ldan ye shes te /
NG0569:215: de nyid rang byung ye shes te //
NG0569:216: sangs rgyas kun gyi snying po'o //
NG0569:217: de nyid rang gi sems nyid de //
NG0569:218: rang sems ma bcos mnyam par bzhag / rig pa brdal khyab ngos bzung med //
NG0569:219: cir snang ye shes ngo bor shar //
NG0569:220: ma yengs ji bzhin ngang gnas na //
NG0569:221: mdzad spyod ma chags blang dor med //
NG0569:222: ma bsgrubs chos sku lhun gyis grub //
NG0569:225: 'gro ba las dag thams cad la //
NG0569:226: mngon par snang de don mdzad do //
NG0569:228: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa snying po gsang ba'i rgyud las /
NG0569:229: mthar thug de kho na nyid kyi le'u ste dgu
NG0569:230: brgya bzhi'o // // de nas rdo rje 'chang chen
NG0569:231: gyis / drag po las kyi rim pa bshad //
NG0569:232: phung sa gsum gyi 'brub khung ni //
NG0569:233: gru gsum rgya dpangs khru mtho gang *//
NG0569:234: kha khyer dang po thod rlon 'phreng *//
NG0569:235: bar pa mtsher rtsa srin mo 'gros //
NG0569:236: mtha' ma gdug pa'i sbrul rigs bzhi //
NG0569:237: phyi nang dug khrag sna tshogs drug / dgra la
NG0569:238: rgyu rten drug ling ga / bgegs la gang gnod
NG0569:239: rdzas kyi gzugs // mtho gang dbang po dod par bya //
NG0569:240: gro ga ming byang khong par brnag / tsha ba gsum dang dug sna tshogs *//
NG0569:241: nad khrag sna tshogs byug par bya //
NG0569:242: khram thod bcug la dong du brnag / dug rgod sbyang dug ra dug pa //
NG0569:243: 'ol mo re lcag ba spru ba //
NG0569:244: mon pa kha byung thod par bsham //
NG0569:245: mi yi nang khrag sna tshogs dang *//
NG0569:246: gcan gzan sna tshogs ra khyi rta //
NG0569:247: khrag sna snying sna gri thod sbyar //
NG0569:248: yungs kar yungs nag ske tshe dang *//
NG0569:249: ji tse shang tse rdo lcags zangs //
NG0569:250: phye gsum rabs chad thod par sbyar //
NG0569:251: gri thod lcags phur seng ldeng mchog phur pa dug khrag ngar blud bsham //
NG0569:252: bdag nyid dpal chen he ru ka / las byed pho nya sprul pa'i tshogs //
NG0569:253: shin tu rngam khros mi bzod pas //
NG0569:254: srog gcod sha za khrag 'thung bsam //
NG0569:255: des ni brnag pa gang yin pa //
NG0569:256: rang dbang med bkug rten la bstim //
NG0569:257: ling ga dgra bgegs dngos su bsam //
NG0569:258: dug thun bud med 'jigs tshul rngam //
NG0569:259: khrag thun sha za srin po'i tshogs //
NG0569:260: 'bru phye mon dang mon mo'i tshogs //
NG0569:261: shin tu 'jigs khros mtshon cha thogs //
NG0569:262: nad kyi bskal pa 'bebs byed cing *//
NG0569:263: dgra bgegs srog gcod sha za bsam //
NG0569:264: phur pa khro bo'i 'jigs tshul rngam //
NG0569:265: smad dbal lcags sa thog ltar bsam //
NG0569:266: drag sngags brgya thun stong thun dbab //
NG0569:267: srog lus rdul phran brlags par bsam //
NG0569:268: de nas phur pas gdab par bya //
NG0569:269: srog lus go cha phyag rgyar bskyed //
NG0569:270: 'di ltar drag sngags sbyor ba yis //
NG0569:271: tshangs pa'i tshe dang ldan pa yang *//
NG0569:273: dgra bgegs rnams la smos ci dgos //
NG0569:274: ma ma trag rag sha kha lding nag mo //
NG0569:275: rag mo shan pa dgra bo la ma ra ya dza dza //
NG0569:276: rag sha rbad ling dgra bo snying khrag tshal pa rbad /
NG0569:277: ru tra ma tra ma ra ya ha li ha
NG0569:278: li dgra bo la dun b+h+yo ma ra ya rbad
NG0569:279: / badzra ki li ya tig sna ha na ha na nri ma ra ya rbad /
NG0569:280: bsad pa dregs pa can la gtad /
NG0569:281: gzir ba bka' gnyan mgon pi la'o //
NG0569:282: thun 'phangs sprul pas nad mtshon dbab //
NG0569:283: nad byo sngags mthar skabs kyis brdeb //
NG0569:284: drod tshad ldan byas myur du 'grub //
NG0569:285: bskal pa nyi shu'i tha ma la //
NG0569:287: rgyas mu stegs bdag gzhan sdes //
NG0569:288: lha srin dregs sngags pho mo rnams //
NG0569:289: mthu rtsal stobs ldan dmod pa 'bor //
NG0569:290: sprul pa sha zan skar ltar 'khrug / dmod ba'i mtshon cha char ltar 'bab //
NG0569:291: byin brlabs mthu stobs me ltar 'bar //
NG0569:292: sngags pa rdo rje dme 'thab byed //
NG0569:293: de tsho rang gi byed sdebs sngags //
NG0569:294: phyir la bzlog cing de nyid bsad //
NG0569:296: rang bzhin rnam dag chos nyid las //
NG0569:297: brub yig dmar nag yongs gyur las //
NG0569:298: dbang drag 'khor lo rtsibs bcug pa //
NG0569:299: rno la rgya chen me 'bar ba //
NG0569:300: lte ba hu~m yig yongs gyur las //
NG0569:301: dpal chen bud d+ha he ru ka / yab yum sangs rgyas dbang phyug ma //
NG0569:302: gsal rdzogs bsgom pa'i thugs kha nas //
NG0569:303: rtsibs bcu'i gdan la hu~m bcu 'phros //
NG0569:304: de dag yongs su gyur pa las //
NG0569:305: shar rtsibs badzra he ru ka / khro mo rdo rje dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:306: lho rtsibs rat+na he ru ka / khro mo rin chen dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:307: nub rtsibs pad+ma he ru ka khro mo dbang phyug pad+ma bsgom //
NG0569:308: byang rtsibs karma he ru ka / khro mo las kyi dbang phyug bsgom //
NG0569:309: shar lho gshin rje mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:310: lho nub shes rab mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:311: nub byang pad+ma mthar byed gnas //
NG0569:312: steng rtsibs gtsug gtor 'khor lo sgyur //
NG0569:313: ser nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pa //
NG0569:314: spyan gsum mche gtsigs rin chen brgyan //
NG0569:315: 'khor lo ral gri phyag na bsnams //
NG0569:316: lha chen gdan la brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:317: 'og rtsibs rdo rje hu~m mdzad de //
NG0569:318: mthing nag zhal gcig phyag gnyis pas //
NG0569:319: rdo rje dgra sta phyag na bsnams //
NG0569:320: ma bdud gdan brkyang bskum bzhugs //
NG0569:321: ye shes 'khor lo spyan drangs bstim //
NG0569:322: dbang bskur byin brlabs skye mched brlab //
NG0569:323: phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul //
NG0569:324: bdud rtsi myang zhing bstod pa bya //
NG0569:326: drag tu 'khor zhing gang dmigs pa'i //
NG0569:327: lha srung rig sngags bcad bzlog gsad //
NG0569:328: de bzhin dur khrod rab la bri //
NG0569:329: rtsibs bzhi lte bar hu~m bcu gcig / mu khyud nang mar rtsa ba'i sngags //
NG0569:330: phyi mar spu bri'i drag sngags dgos //
NG0569:331: rig sngags drag po smra bcad bzlas //
NG0569:332: bdud bzhi nyon mongs dug lnga gcad //
NG0569:334: bsrung dang bzlog dang bsad pa dang *//
NG0569:335: byang chub bsgrub pa'i las rnams 'grub //
NG0569:336: rgyu rten ling ga ming byang bcas //
NG0569:337: snying khar mtshon cha'i 'khor lo gzhug sgrub khang rgyun srang rten la mnan //
NG0569:338: de dag gsang sngags 'di lta ste //
NG0569:339: na ma sa man ta ka ya ba ka tsit+ta badzra he ru ka ni /
NG0569:340: om a hu~m badzra ma ha kro d+ha ra dza ya /
NG0569:341: shri he he ru ru ka ka ma ha tsan d+ha u kra ye hu~m /
NG0569:342: badzra kro d+ha pa la ti ma ha kro d+ha ra dza ya /
NG0569:344: ma ha kro d+hi shwa ri ma ha yo gi ni tsin+da da ki ni /
NG0569:362: 'khor lo bskor zhing sngags bzlas pas /
NG0569:363: 'byung ba'i rgyun kyang phyir bzlog na /
NG0569:364: sngags byang sbod gtong smos ci dgos /
NG0569:365: rang 'khor bsrung zhing nyon mongs gcod /
NG0569:366: bla med byang chub yang dag thob /
NG0569:368: 'jam dpal khri drug stong pa rdo rje snying po'i rgyud las /
NG0569:369: drag po'i 'khor lo'i gsang ba'i le'u ste dgu brgya
NG0569:370: lnga pa'o // // de nas ya ma ra dza
NG0569:372: sangs rgyas bstan pa bsrung ba'i phyir //
NG0569:373: don po lha srin dregs pa la //
NG0569:374: gtad pa'i sbyor ba bshad du gsol //
NG0569:375: de skad gsol pas bka' stsal pa //
NG0569:376: zhus don ngas bshad khyod nyon cig / brnag pa lha srin dregs pa la //
NG0569:377: gtad pa'i rim pa rnam pa gnyis //
NG0569:378: pho la gtad dang mo la gtad //
NG0569:379: pho la gtad pa brgyad yin te //
NG0569:380: las kyi gshin rje la gtad dang *//
NG0569:381: lha la gtad dang bdud la gtad //
NG0569:382: rgyal po la gtad btsan la gtad //
NG0569:383: gnod sbyin la gtad klu la gtad //
NG0569:385: gshin rje la gtad sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:386: zhing lpags rten 'brel rdzas kyis byug / dug khrag sgro rtsas 'khor lo bri //
NG0569:387: dbus su brnag pa'i ming byang gzugs //
NG0569:388: rtsibs bcur drag sngags grangs phyed dgos //
NG0569:389: gshin rje nag por lto bar bri //
NG0569:390: rgyu rten ling ga spyi rus cas //
NG0569:391: 'khor lo tshil chen gu gul byug / mi rta la sogs snying sna tshogs //
NG0569:392: dam rdzas sha khrag gtor ma bsham //
NG0569:393: gsur chen btang zhing drag sngags bzlas //
NG0569:394: nag po 'jigs tshul be con thogs //
NG0569:395: ling ga dgra bo'i dngos su bsams //
NG0569:396: srog gcod sha za khrag 'thung gsod //
NG0569:397: gshin rje'i bskul ba gang rung btang *//
NG0569:398: dur khrod lhor bltas dmyal chu khol //
NG0569:399: tsha sgo khu rlangs ngam grog dmar //
NG0569:400: der ni 'khor lo ling ga mang *//
NG0569:401: de la las bcol gnyer gtad bya *//
NG0569:402: des ni yun rings mi thogs pa //
NG0569:403: gang gtad glang thabs nad kyis gsod //
NG0569:404: om a kro to ka ya man ta hri ti ka la rus pa hu~m phat /
NG0569:405: ni ya ma ra tsa ni /
NG0569:406: khug drol shri kro d+ha ha b+hi dza ya khams thums //
NG0569:408: 'gal byed gtso bo kam kar thums /
NG0569:417: om shri many+dzu ya ma ra dza sa to me yang yam yam thum thum /
NG0569:418: dgra bo'i snying la dun b+h+yo /
NG0569:420: lha la gtod pa'i sbyor ba ni //
NG0569:421: dur khrod ras la rdzas kyis byug / 'khor lo rtsibs bcu'i sngags rnams ming *//
NG0569:422: ling ga ming byang bya rgod 'brong *//
NG0569:423: lug dkar ra sha'i sha khrag snying *//
NG0569:425: dkar gsum mngar gsum gtor ma @#//
NG0569:428: sngags bzlas gsur gtang lha chen bskul //
NG0569:429: ling ga dgra srog srog gcod gsod //
